  "about": [
    "An avid collector, Bulent heads the Istanbul Foundation for Culture and Arts and the Istanbul Modern Art Foundation, which includes the Istanbul Modern Art Museum.",
    "In Turkish, Eczacibasi means \"chief pharmacist,\" an honorary title and surname given to Bulent's grandfather, Suleyman Ferit Eczacibasi."
